g.text: The Initialization, Pre-Processing, and Post-Processing tables
contain detailed information about business rules (Table 5.25).
Business rules that appear in these tables must necessarily fall
within the business rule engine’s Effective Rule Scope (Book I,
§5.4.5), i.e., the rule must be Active, the journey must be part of
the specified portfolio, the execution’s optimization date-time
must occur within the rule’s effectivity interval, etc.
